                  </hi>. I am sister of Maria Hendry—She has one sister in partnership with her—they live in Portland-street—on the 3rd August, I was standing in their shop about three o'clock in the afternoon—the pri<lb></lb>soner ran to the door, took this shawl from the window, put it under his coat, and ran away with it—he was brought back by a gentleman with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-576" type="witnessName">
